{"tid":1916639,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"DSE生棄北上 赴台升學意欲急增","createTime":"2020-03-09T03:54:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T04:34:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c0937498e7d3b3591d4807c4aac5b7838547a981","tid":1916639,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:54:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200309/OUEZSHNBH76NXQHOQCNLV4HWH4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200309%2FOUEZSHNBH76NXQHOQCNLV4HWH4%2F&d=rROtLXfiIyO0AijGL7caMxvMbnGxJ%2B6Vh8biNj9iadw%3D&h=d89b8d7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200309%2FOUEZSHNBH76NXQHOQCNLV4HWH4%2F&h=50c6ee28\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200309/OUEZSHNBH76NXQHOQCNLV4HWH4/</a><br />\n<br />\nDSE生棄北上 赴台升學意欲急增<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200309/large/1583685831_39c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200309%2Flarge%2F1583685831_39c1.jpg&h=d8e3af08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n學友社調查發現30%文憑試考生擬赴台升學，只有15%考慮負笈內地。黃耀興攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】逆權運動啟發港人再一次覺醒，對中國的腐敗與暴政深惡痛絕。學友社一項調查發現，本港學生選擇境外升學地點時，更看重政治環境及制度因素，因而放棄升學內地。相反，基於同樣理由，較多學生選擇台灣升學。學友社相信，武漢肺炎對學生考慮內地升學影響不大，因為他們對內地政治信心已在社會事件中反映出來。<br />\n<br />\n憂慮內地政治環境<br />\n<br />\n學友社於2019年12月至2020年2月期間，以問卷調查形式成功訪問1,308名應屆文憑試考生，了解他們前往內地及台灣升學的意向。調查發現，表示「考慮內地升學」比例較去年下降5個百分點至15%，而「考慮台灣升學」的比例則上升8個百分點至30%，學生對兩地的差距達一倍。<br />\n<br />\n考慮到內地升學的學生當中，最多人考慮到收生要求較低，佔60%。而不考慮到內地升學的學生當中，最多人考慮政治環境及制度因素，佔69%，比去年增加32個百分點；其次是生活環境較香港差，佔37%，比去年增加8個百分點。考慮升學台灣的學生中，有49%認同台灣的文化及地理位置與香港相近，比去年增加14個百分點；37%學生認同台灣的政治環境及制度，增加20個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n學友社學生輔導顧問吳寶城指出，學生對兩地的升學意欲，明顯受2019下半年社會事件影響，學生選擇升學地點時更看重政治環境及制度。吳寶城認為，學生在升學考慮上，除了要考慮宏觀環境，亦要注意課程內容、學習模式及認受性等微觀因素作綜合考慮，而且升學選擇是一個長遠決定，不應該太受個別短期因素影響。<br />\n<br />\n■記者何嘉瑤<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200309/large/1583685831_d374.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200309%2Flarge%2F1583685831_d374.jpg&h=f91ae978&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d78c0226c564137cabf7607d68875e7ea2d35e4","tid":1916639,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:55:14.000Z","msg":"學友社<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d23f0ded02308e116467d295f955cc6360bd8854","tid":1916639,"uid":29835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:55:56.000Z","msg":"15%入面有幾多係新移民"},{"pid":"24361504a91fafa8c5e2c43e0a6ab19bac245a82","tid":1916639,"uid":315761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:57:12.000Z","msg":"學友社係支共地下組織"},{"pid":"6c042692cff72a74e843d2d7651e1503fae5a8d7","tid":1916639,"uid":225347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d23f0ded02308e116467d295f955cc6360bd8854","tid":1916639,"uid":29835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:55:56.000Z","msg":"15%入面有幾多係新移民"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T04:08:21.000Z","msg":"全部"},{"pid":"a0ce2f2ccb30becedd5566ffe1be22750b654895","tid":1916639,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c042692cff72a74e843d2d7651e1503fae5a8d7","tid":1916639,"uid":225347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d23f0ded02308e116467d295f955cc6360bd8854","tid":1916639,"uid":29835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:55:56.000Z","msg":"15%入面有幾多係新移民"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T04:08:21.000Z","msg":"全部"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T04:34:35.000Z","msg":"哈哈，新移民先好<br />\n真．香港學生唔使同班賤畜爭位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好